'''老品语'''是一种在中国[[云南省|云南省]][[勐海县|勐海县]]勐遮镇曼洪村曼品村（或老品村）使用的[[彝语|彝语]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vdefault.aspx?departmentid=144437 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-20 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130190308/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vdefault.aspx?departmentid=144437 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="12bn">{{Cite web |date=2011-12-15 |script-title=zh:老品人、八甲人民族归属问题尘埃落定 |url=http://www.12bn.net/article/article_3982.html |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130185936/http://www.12bn.net/article/article_3982.html |archive-date=2016-11-30 |access-date=2016-11-30 |website=12bn.net |language=zh}}</ref>

在勐连县的1,300名族人中有不到1,000名使用者。<ref name="Bradley2007">{{Cite book |last=Bradley |first=David |title=Language Diversity Endangered |publisher=Mouton de Gruyter |year=2007 |editor-last=Brenzinger |editor-first=Matthias |location=New York |chapter=Language Endangerment in China and Mainland Southeast Asia}}</ref>他们被划为[[傣族|傣族]]。<ref name="12bn" />

